caption.p: Effect of COME on the activity of NF-κB/AP-1 in LPS-stimulated THP-1-XBlue™-MD2-CD14 cells. Cells were pre-treated in indicated concentrations by COME, prednisone or only solvent (DMSO) for 1 h, after that, LPS was added and NF-κB/AP-1 activity was measured 24 h later. ** indicates statistical significance to positive control (DMSO) p < 0.01, **** indicates statistical significance to positive control (DMSO) p < 0.0001.
